\begin_layout Itemize
The goal: to evaluate the optimal regulation on enforcement of non-compete
 agreements from a welfare perspective.
 E.g., veil of ignorance, the welfare of an agent who does not know whether
 he will be an entrepreneur or a worker.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
The methodology: study welfare from different policies through the lens
 of a structural model.
 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
