\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Seems like sorting of spinoff / entrepreneurial-oriented workers to non-enforcin
g regimes, and identifying these workers with the relevant workers in the
 Michigan data, would generate implications along these lines.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Need to add funding to the model - spinoffs require both entrepreneurs able
 to form them and funding.
